### 3.3 Justification of Performance Metrics

Performance metrics were chosen based on the system's intended purpose and risk classification.
Confidence scores reflect the model's certainty in its predictions. Latency is tracked to ensure
the system meets real-time operational requirements. Error rates capture system reliability.

_Provider should supplement with domain-specific accuracy metrics (e.g., precision, recall, F1
for the target detection classes)._

